, Ketua DPRD Kota Bekasi  menyerahkan bantuan kepada korban banjir berupa makanan, minuman, dan alat kebersihan lainnya.","post_time":1741323318,"owner":"57475572529","username":"wibawa.media","comment_count":1,"like_count":24,"cdn_image":"//cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/pemkotbekasi/photo_gallery/picture/57475572529/DG4qf0eT3T3.jpg"},{"id":"DG2VyE-TuHO","image":"https://scontent-fra5-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.2885-15/482944934_18302556250230422_3438032757388267648_n.webp?stp=dst-webp_p720x720&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6IkZFRUQuaW1hZ2VfdXJsZ2VuLjE0NDB4MTgwMC5zZHIuZjc1NzYxLmRlZmF1bHRfaW1hZ2UifQ&_nc_ht=scontent-fra5-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=102&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2QEjUNfPwpw2lVvat0_KazWBRyZ8BxVyktG2zenZAwFWNFKoXOC4MDAOJvWxsyeOSWM&_nc_ohc=bMYd_6h1MbgQ7kNvwGVxnKJ&_nc_gid=Kye6D5SDoklQnBhXjKznJw&edm=APoiHPcBAAAA&ccb=7-5&ig_cache_key=MzU4MjE0NjM1MzkxMDcwMjU0Mg%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&oh=00_AfPRLJFLVNmdZpwi1SNu2F8ooEVEBMvnWj6d4BhmNLe2LA&oe=68682E56&_nc_sid=22de04","caption":"Kami segenap pimpinan dan anggota DPRD Kota Bekasi, turut berduka cita atas bencana banjir yang melanda Kota Bekasi.\n\nSemoga diberikan kesabaran dan musibah ini segera berlalu.\n\n#DPRDKotaBekasi #kotabekasi","post_time":1741245143,"owner":"57475572529","username":"wibawa.media","comment_count":1,"like_count":31,"cdn_image":"//cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/pemkotbekasi/photo_gallery/picture/57475572529/DG2VyE-TuHO.jpg"}]